cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with depth map super-resolution using machine learning and variational methods. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The use of deep convolutional networks for super-resolution also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of synthetic data generation hints at a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
